%% Observability and Telemetry Flow
flowchart TD
    api[Cloud Run API] --> logApi[Structured Logs]
    worker[Cloud Run Worker] --> logWorker[Structured Logs]
    web[Blazor Web] --> logWeb[Structured Logs]

    logApi --> cloudLogging[Cloud Logging]
    logWorker --> cloudLogging
    logWeb --> cloudLogging

    api --> trace[Cloud Trace]
    worker --> trace

    cloudLogging --> monitoring[Cloud Monitoring]
    cloudLogging --> errorReporting[Error Reporting]

    monitoring --> dashboard[Operational Dashboard]
    monitoring --> alerts[Alerts]

    alerts --> A1[Transcription failure rate high]
    alerts --> A2[Vertex AI latency high]
    alerts --> A3[Pub/Sub retry count high]
    alerts --> A4[Cloud Run error rate high]
    alerts --> A5[Cloud SQL connection errors]

    dashboard --> M1[Upload duration]
    dashboard --> M2[Processing duration]
    dashboard --> M3[Speech-to-Text duration]
    dashboard --> M4[Gemini prompt latency]
    dashboard --> M5[Cost-sensitive AI calls]
